OL,3,CFormer Corrie star Sally Lindsay
OL,4,Cawarded MBE
OL,6,FFormer Coronation Street star Sally
OL,7,FLindsay has been made a Member of the
OL,8,FOrder of the British Empire (MBE) in
OL,9,Fthe King's New Year Honours list.
OL,11,FThe 52-year old, best known for
OL,12,Fplaying the long-suffering Rovers
OL,13,FReturn landlady Shelley Unwin on the
OL,14,FITV soap, was recognised for her
OL,15,Fservices to drama.
OL,17,FThe Stockport-born actress began her
OL,18,Fcareer in theatre and landed her first
OL,19,FTV gig in 2000, appearing in sitcom
OL,20,FThe Royle Family, before starring in
OL,21,FFat Friends and Phoenix Nights.
