OL,3,CFormer Corrie star Sally Lindsay
OL,4,Cawarded MBE
OL,6,FShe later starred on Corrie from 2001
OL,7,Funtil 2006, with her character's
OL,8,Fbiggest storylines including being at
OL,9,Fthe centre of the psychological and
OL,10,Fphysical abuse of her boyfriend,
OL,11,FCharlie Stubbs, played by Bill Ward,
OL,12,Fwho she eventually leaves at the alter.
OL,14,FThe role won her the Inside Soap award
OL,15,Ffor best actress in 2005.
