OL,3,CFormer Corrie star Sally Lindsay
OL,4,Cawarded MBE
OL,6,FAfter five years on the cobbles,
OL,7,FLindsay went back to theatre and
OL,8,Fstarred in the 2008 production of
OL,9,FShelagh Delaney's A Taste Of Honey at
OL,10,Fthe Royal Exchange Theatre in
OL,11,FManchester.
OL,13,FIn 2011, she co-created and starred in
OL,14,FITV's Scott & Bailey, alongside
OL,15,FSuranne Jones and Lesley Sharp, about
OL,16,Ftwo detectives specialising in murder
OL,17,Fcases at a Manchester police unit.
