OL,3,CFormer Corrie star Sally Lindsay
OL,4,Cawarded MBE
OL,6,FShe went on to star in the Sky sitcom
OL,7,FMount Pleasant from 2011 until 2017
OL,8,Fbefore starring in Cold Call, a crime
OL,9,Fdrama about a single mother who
OL,10,Fbecomes a victim of fraud.
OL,12,FShe more recently co-created and
OL,13,Fstarred in the Channel 5 drama, The
OL,14,FMadame Blanc Mysteries, about a
OL,15,FBritish antiques dealer who solves
OL,16,Fmysteries in the south of France.
