OL,3,CFormer Corrie star Sally Lindsay
OL,4,Cawarded MBE
OL,6,FAlongside her writing and acting
OL,7,Fcareer, Lindsay is also an ambassador
OL,8,Ffor Demelza Hospice Care, a charity
OL,9,Fwhich provides support for children
OL,10,Fwith serious or life-limiting
OL,11,Fconditions and their families.
OL,13,FAppearing as a panellist on ITV's
OL,14,FLoose Women, Lindsay has also fronted
OL,15,Fa number of documentaries.
