OL,4,Cawarded MBE
OL,6,FShe is also the president of Women Of
OL,7,FThe Year Luncheon and awards which
OL,8,Faims to "promote positive female role
OL,9,Fmodels" across all areas of society
OL,10,Fand business community while also
OL,11,Fraising money for charity.
OL,13,FLindsay is the creative director of
OL,14,FSaffron Cherry Productions where she
OL,15,Fhelps to "develop strong stories as
OL,16,Fwell as advocating for powerful female
OL,17,Froles."
